<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1922-01-28T14:00:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1922-01-28T14:00:00-05:00" n="856" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d856">
                        <note rend="inline" type="source">892.6363/9: Telegram</note>
                        <head><hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to
                                the Chargé in Siam</hi> (<persName type="to"><hi rend="italic">Williams</hi></persName>)</head>
                        <opener><dateline rendition="#right"><placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1922-01-28T14:00:00-05:00"><hi rend="italic">January 28,
                                        1922—2 p.m.</hi></date></dateline></opener>
                        <p>6. Your 198 December 1, 200 December 6, and 3 January 11.</p>
                        <p>Make no further representations until instructed and avoid becoming
                            involved in private negotiations or in controversy.</p>
                        <closer><signed><hi rend="smallcaps">Hughes</hi></signed></closer>
                    </div>
                </body></text></TEI>